data.description:
Indulge in prestige with this gated City of Atlantis gem. Situated on a corner lot, this split floor plan oasis is designed for luxury living.  The custom kitchen, adorned with fine cabinetry and granite countertops, beckons culinary delights. An entertainer's dream, it features a Florida room with a den/office area. Full hurricane impact windows & doors for your security. Custom window blinds throughout the home. Never worry about power outages with a whole-house natural gas generator. Lushly landscaped yard, and the in-ground heated pool enclosed in a large screened-in patio offer a private retreat. Three driveways provide plenty of parking room for your guests. This residence marries elegance and practicality in the heart of Atlantis - your gateway to sophisticated living. Further home features include a brand-new central a/c installed December 2023 which covers the main house. New electrical panel 2020. 
The City of Atlantis is a gated and well-maintained community offering 2 championship golf courses with no membership requirements. Another benefit of the city is Kintz Park, a great place to play tennis, pickleball or attend a party or one of the city's annual sponsored events such as the Spring Fling, Egg Hunt, the Holiday Golf Cart parade, etc. The community park club room can be reserved for your birthday parties or private events. Kintz Park has picnic areas and a water park for a fun time for your family and guests! Atlantis is conveniently located close to the area's best beaches, shopping centers & restaurants, I-95, the turnpike to the West, and the Palm Beach International airport. The City of Atlantis features its own police department.
